I’ve had many friends who have come and gone throughout my life. Of the few friends that have stood by me through thick and thin, there’s none that I’m as close to as you.

You always tell me that I am the strongest and bravest person you know. You always say that you admire my courage for taking risks and starting from nothing. But the truth is, I have that strength because I have you. I know you would not let me fall, and if I do, you will always be there to catch me. You are the brave one, you just haven’t realized that yet. Today, I am wishing you all the good things this world has to offer because your heart contains nothing but goodness. Wonderful bday!

Well first of all its been soo hard to decide on the right picture to post. I choose the first one we have ever taken together thinking it was the most special of all because it marks the beginning of us.
You are one of a kind, with your craziness and your beautiful soul you tend to enlighten peoples life.
Someone said happiness is made of small moments, we cant understand the true value of it if we dont go through hardships. You are the most strong woman i know, you are a  fighter who doesnt know the option of losing soo i will wish you all the happiness of the world knowing you wont ever brake down from stupid stuff. I cant wait to meet your crazy ass and go around as a double trouble again. #myblondieisbetterthanyours #itsmyblondiesbirthday

People tend to take everything for granted. They tend to give you love only on special days forgetting whats really important. They dont value every bit of time. On this special day im the one lucky to be able to celebrate it with you. You are someone as rare as a desert rose, im blessed to have you in my life, someone who doesnt give our relationship for granted, someone caring and supporting who has been through a lot of things with me, who gives me love in his own way in every moment and not just once a year.
I wish you the best of everything life can offer. Yours xx
